I hope you like the program. It couldn't have been written without the
support and feed-back from a rather large number of ppl. 

I tried the patience of my girlfriend sorely, and am very grateful
for the support provided by the following ppl. This is by no means a
complete list, just the highlights. If I have missed someone, please
let me know.

	Michael. (oreillym@tartarus.uwa.edu.au).
	(now michael@iinet.com.au)

Bill C. Riemers (bcr@physics.purdue.edu)
	Stuck my fingers in everywhere and hacked term all to pieces.
	You are using the remains of it right now.
	Also added TitanOS support and termnet.

David Wexelblat (dwex@mtgzfs3.att.com)
	Write the extensive mods for SYSV support.

David Dawes (dawes@physics.su.oz.au)
	Debugged the above. 

